          <p>Have conversations that matter to you. Specify topic preferences and get relevant conversation prompts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a class="info-card info-card-3">
      <div class="front info-card">
        <h2>Go at your own pace</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="back info-card">
        <div>
          <p>Sessions are only 15 minutes long. Take as many or as few as you want!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

